quote.summary: Hollwin Urban Operation Service Group Co Ltd is a China-based company principally engaged in the provision of urban service and operation. The Company primarily operates its businesses through three segments. Property Management Services segment is mainly engaged in the provision of management and operation services provided to commercial properties, residential properties, and public properties. City Services segment is mainly involved in the provision of lighting system operation services, municipal sanitation services, landscaping and engineering services, parking lot operation services and sublease of parking lot. Commercial Operation Services segment is mainly involved in the provision of commercial operation services such as tenant sourcing services, tenant management, rent collection services and sublease of commercial properties.
